annotation.TEXT: So, it's a pipe, and I guess I'm supposed to go down it. But, what if I don't wanna go down it?
However, it just leads to the same place as the first pipe. I bet these pipes are really there to allow you a chance to retry the flying part without dying if you screw up, which is nice.
And there's a key... Hmm...
And that just takes me to this point. Once again, backtracking from here probably isn't a good idea.
So... nothing? Maybe if I wait for the P-switch to expire...
